name: MiDi Clutch: from the For Anne Collection
description:
The For Anne collection is an exclusive limited edition, hand crafted quality fashion bag. All bags are made using the finest quality materials. These materials are vibrant and relevant, with the design focusing on quality, colour, texture, wearability and durability.

Available in the following colours: 
QUINCE (YELLOW PATTERNED)
AZURE (BLUE PATTERNED)
AMBER (ORANGE PATTERNED)
MOCHA & QUINCE (BROWN & YELLOW PATTERNED)
MOCHA & AZURE (BROWN & BLUE PATTERNED)

The unique shape is the feature throughout the mid sized bags in this Taybian Design collection. The handle is designed for comfort, gives the bag structure and is aesthetically gorgeous. This larger clutch can be used as an everyday bag, as it can carry a deceiving amount inside. This bag is so versatile that it can also be used to accessorise an evening gown. Dress it up or dress it casual. Itâ€™s your choice!

 

Size indication: 450mmx300mmx60mm

name: 'Jasper' - Midi
description:
The JASPER Midi Handbag is hand crafted from beautiful soft upholstery fabric. 

The utmost care is taken in the construction and all bags have been thoroughly tested for comfort and durability.

Designed for aesthetic and comfort!
The strap is specifically designed to distribute the weight of the bags contents. 
You can 'hide' a surprising amount in these beautiful bags, being also designed to specifically to hide the bulk. Therefore you can carry the kitchen sink!

There is no 'clasp' to close the bag, all Midi bags have hidden magnets to self close the bag opening. Clever!

The bags dimensions are approximately: 
width (at base) 500mm / width (at opening) 250mm
height 300mm
depth 60mm
strap 450mm

Every bag purchased comes packed in its very own complimentary Taybian Calico Carry Bag.
